  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;23:14">Use the <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;23:30">--output</codeph> option to write one report file
  per validated document to a directory. This is useful for sharing results with
  your team, uploading reports as CI artifacts, or tracking quality over time.</shortdesc>

  <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="taskbody:1;27:13">

    <prereq id="prereq" class="- topic/section task/prereq " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="prereq:1;29:25">
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="p:1;30:10">Decide on a format for the saved reports before running the command.
      <xref href="t_set-output-format.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="xref:1;31:45" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?>Set output format<?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">Use the <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_set-output-format.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;24:30">--format</codeph> option to choose how   markdown-validator presents its report: plain text for terminal reading,   JSON for CI integration and scripting, or CSV for spreadsheet analysis.</desc></xref> compares the text, JSON,
      and CSV options.</p>
    </prereq>

    <context id="context" class="- topic/section task/context " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="context:1;35:27">
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="p:2;36:10">Use case by format: <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="b:1;36:33">JSON</b> — CI artifact upload and scripting;
      <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="b:2;37:10">CSV</b> — quality tracking and spreadsheet import; <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="b:3;37:64">text</b> — ad-hoc
      team review. The output directory is created automatically if it does not
      exist.</p>
    </context>

