      <step id="step-review-output" class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="step:2;73:37">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="cmd:2;74:14">Open the output directory to confirm the generated files.</cmd>
        <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="info:2;75:15">
          <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="p:4;76:14">Each report file is named after the source document. For example,
          validating <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="filepath:4;77:32">docs/tutorial-deploy-app.md</filepath> with
          <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="codeph:3;78:19">--format json</codeph> produces
          <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="filepath:5;79:21">reports/tutorial-deploy-app.json</filepath>. With
          <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="codeph:4;80:19">--format csv</codeph> it produces
          <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="filepath:6;81:21">reports/tutorial-deploy-app.csv</filepath>.</p>
          <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="p:5;82:14">If you validate a directory, the output directory mirrors only the
          filenames — subdirectory paths from the source are not recreated. All
          report files land in the single output directory you specified.</p>
        </info>
      </step>

      <step id="step-name-convention" class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_save-reports.dita" xtrc="step:3;88:39">
